<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[باب الحاء والتاء]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[الحاء والتاء والراء]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">حتر:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الحَتْرُ:</span> الذَّكَرُ من الثَّعالِبِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والحِتَارُ:</span> ما اسْتَدَارَ بالعَيْن من باطِنِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> الجَفْن.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وحِتَارُ الظُّفرِ:</span> ما أحَاطَ به. وكذلك حَلْقَةُ الدُّبُر.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والحِتَارُ:</span> طُنُبٌ من أطْنابِ الخَيْمَةِ.<span class="c5"> وهو أيضاً:</span> كِفَافُ الثَّوْبِ،<span class="c5"> وجَمْعُه:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>حُتُرٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وما حَتَرْتُ اليَوْمَ شَيْئاً:</span> أي ما ذُقْتُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وحَتَرَهُ:</span> قاتَه.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">والحُتْرَةُ:</span> طَعَامُ البِنَاءِ، حَتَّرَ لنا حُتْرةً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">والحَتْرُ:</span> القَتْرُ.<span class="c5"> والحَاتِرُ:</span> القاتِرُ.<span class="c5"> والإِحْتَارُ:</span> الإِقْتَارُ.<span class="c5"> وحَتَرْتُ له شَيْئاً:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>أعْطَيْتَه قَليلاً، وهو حَاتِرٌ ومُحْتِرٌ أيضاً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">والمُحْتَرُ:</span> المُحْكَمُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في ك: باطل.</p> </div>